  "component_name": "Action/Option Generator",
  "primary_agent": "Hermes",
  "function": "Generates potential initial actions/observations: 1. Focus on towering architecture (Wayne Tower). 2. Notice the high-tech security contrasted with old gothic hints elsewhere. 3. Sense underlying 'fear' or 'desire' despite the calm surface (using Qi Men subtly). 4. Simply observe the flow of wealthy people. Introduce a minor event: Distant siren, dropped newspaper, flicker of an odd reflection.",
